ShareOverviewSummaryLevel 3 Financing, Inc. has worked on one contract worth $34,427 USD in obligations from the federal government since FY2007. In its latest active fiscal year (2014), the organization received a total of $34,428 USD in obligations.The sole agency it has contracted with is the Department of Veterans Affairs.

